\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\qj\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe1033\hich\f5\fs20\lang1033\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\b0{\*\cs28\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i Reader:}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0  {\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 24.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature according to its kind, quadrupeds and reptiles and wild beasts of the earth according to their kind, and it was so. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 25.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God made the wild beasts of the earth according to their kin
d, and cattle according to their kind, and all the reptiles of the earth according to their kind, and God saw that they were good. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 26.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God said, Let us make man according to our image and likeness, and let them have dominion over the fish of the sea, a
nd over the flying creatures of heaven, and over the cattle and all the earth, and over all the reptiles that creep on the earth. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 27.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God made man, according to the image of God he made him, male and female he made them. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 28.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God blessed them, sayin
g, Increase and multiply and fill the earth and subdue it, and have dominion over the fish of the seas and flying creatures of heaven, and all the cattle and the earth, and all the reptiles that creep on the earth. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 29.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God said, Behold I have given to 
you every seed bearing herb sowing seed which is upon all the earth, and every tree which has in itself the fruit of seed that is sown, to you it shall be for food. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 30.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And to all the wild beasts of the earth, and to all the flying creatures of heaven and 
to every reptile creeping on the earth, which has in itself the breath of life, even every green plant for food; and it was so. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 31.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God saw all the things that he had made, and, behold, they were very good. And there was evening and there was morning, 
the sixth day. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 1.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And the heavens and the earth were finished, and the whole world of them. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 2.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God finished on the sixth day his works which he made, and he ceased on the seventh day from all his works which he made. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 3.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God blessed the seventh day 
and sanctified it, because in it he ceased from all his works which God began to do. }}
