\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\qj\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe1033\hich\f5\fs20\lang1033\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\b0{\*\cs28\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i Reader:}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0  {\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 1.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  My son, if thou wilt receive the utterance of my commandment, and hide it with thee; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 2.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  thine ear shall hearken to wisdom; thou shalt also apply thine heart to understanding, and shalt apply it to the instruction of thy son. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 3.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For if thou shalt
 call to wisdom, and utter thy voice for understanding; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 4.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  and if thou shalt seek it as silver, and search diligently for it as for treasures; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 5.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  then shalt thou understand the fear of the Lord, and find the knowledge of God. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 6.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For the Lord gives wisdom; 
and from his presence come knowledge and understanding, }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 7.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  and he treasures up salvation for them that walk uprightly: he will protect their way; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 8.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  that he may guard the righteous way: and he will preserve the way of them that fear him. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 9.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Then shalt thou
 understand righteousness, and judgment; and shalt direct all thy course aright. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 10.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For if wisdom shall come into thine understanding, and discernment shall seem pleasing to thy soul, }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 11.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  good counsel shall guard thee, and holy understanding shall keep th
ee; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 12.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  to deliver thee from the evil way, and from the man that speaks nothing faithfully. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 13.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Alas for those who forsake right paths, to walk in ways of darkness; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 14.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  who rejoice in evils, and delight in wicked perverseness; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 15.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  whose paths are crooked, 
and their courses winding; }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 16.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  to remove thee far from the straight way, and to estrange thee from a righteous purpose. My son, let not evil counsel overtake thee, }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 17.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  of her who has forsaken the instruction of her youth, and forgotten the covenant of God.
 }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 18.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For she has fixed her house near death, and guided her wheels near Hades with the giants. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 19.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  None that go by her shall return, neither shall they take hold of right paths, for they are not apprehended of the years of life. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 20.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For had they gone in go
od paths, they would have found the paths of righteousness easy. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 21.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For the upright shall dwell in the earth, and the holy shall be left behind in it. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 22.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  The paths of the ungodly shall perish out of the earth, and transgressors shall be driven away from 
it. }}
