\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\qj\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe1033\hich\f5\fs20\lang1033\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\b0{\*\cs28\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i Reader:}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 1.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  My son, forget not my laws; but let thine heart keep my words: }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 2.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  for length of existence, and years of life, and peace, shall they add to thee. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 3.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Let not mercy and truth forsake thee; but bind them about thy neck: }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 4.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  so shalt thou find favor: 
and do thou provide things honest in the sight of the Lord, and of men. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 5.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Trust in God with all thine heart; and be not exalted in thine own wisdom. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 6.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  In all thy ways acquaint thyself with her, that she may rightly direct thy paths. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 7.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Be not wise in thi
ne own conceit; but fear God, and depart from all evil. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 8.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Then shall there be health to thy body, and good keeping to thy bones. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 9.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Honor the Lord with thy just labors, and give him the first of thy fruits of righteousness: }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 10.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  that thy storehouses may be
 completely filled with corn, and that thy presses may burst forth with wine. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 11.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  My son, despise not the chastening of the Lord; nor faint when thou art rebuked of him: }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 12.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  for whom the Lord loves, he rebukes, and scourges every son whom he receives. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 13.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  
Blessed is the man who has found wisdom, and the mortal who knows prudence. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 14.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For it is better to traffic for her, than for treasures of gold and silver. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 15.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And she is more valuable than precious stones: no evil thing shall resist her: she is well known
 to all that approach her, and no precious thing is equal to her in value. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 16.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For length of existence and years of life are in her right hand; and in her left hand are wealth and glory: out of her mouth proceeds righteousness, and she carries law and merc
y upon her tongue. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 17.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Her ways are good ways, and all her paths are peaceful. }{\*\cs30\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033\rtlch\ltrch\hich\fs16\loch\fs16 18.}{\*\cs24\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  She is a tree of life to all that lay hold upon her; and she is a secure help to all that stay themselves on her, as on the Lord. }}
